      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions were reproduced: bovine blood analog (glycerol-water, viscosity 3.5 cP at 37°C), flow rates 2.5–7 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM. All conditions documented in the FDA benchmark protocol; deviations from nominal were within ±3%."
