      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative conditions (flow rates 2.5–7 L/min, blood analog fluid). The validation domain closely matches the COU: Class II CPB device, same operating envelope, same hemolysis QoI. Geometric fidelity was confirmed by CT scan comparison."
